<br>
I don't think it sucks for the level 59 with 1 blue left- He actually has less exp to get till he is 60- He still only need 1 blue, but each blue in 59 costs less.<br>
<br>
I don't think it will suck for those who are 53. A chunk of the exp you would have needed for 54 and 59 should now be in 51 and 52.<br>
<br>
The 54-57 or 58 crowd probably loses a bit of exp- 55, 56, 57, and 58 I would expect to cost more. Sure, some of that is a chunk you would have had to earn in 59 anyway, but a chunk of it is the exp you already earned in 54.<br>
<br>
I expect the just dings 55's to get hit the hardest, but, at least for me, 51-60 took so freaking long anyway that the loss or gain of a small amount of XP probably won't be a big deal.<br>
<br>
Of course, this is all based on my guesses, and have no facts to back em up. The 59 and 54 exp's have to go to 51, 52, 53, 55, 56, 57, and 58.<br>
<br>
Heck, it could even be that 54 was divided up to 52 and 53, while 59 went to 55, 56, 57, and 58- IE, it would take the same amount of exp to go from 1 to 55 as it does now. In that case, no one would lose any at all, and people would only gain exp. Very small amount.<br>
<br>
